Given the following program and the variable in complex data type, decompose the it into variables with primary data type.. The program is 
typedef long a;

fn1() {}

typedef a d __attribute__((__vector_size__(sizeof(long))));

d fn2() {
  long c = fn1;
  d f = {c};
  return f;
}

main() {}
.                 The target to be optimized is `d`: a typedef for a vector of `long`

